<div class="title">Enough Is as Good as a Feast</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Dr.+Demento&Exact=1">Dr. Demento</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Dr. Demento. "Enough Is as Good as a Feast: An Experience with 2C-I (exp30186)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 30, 2004. erowid.org/exp/30186</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

<!-- DoseChart -->
	<table border='2' cellpadding='4' cellspacing='0' bordercolor='#224422' class='dosechart'>
