		 <td width='90' align='right'>DOSE:<br/></td>
		 <td width='90' class='dosechart-amount' align='center'>16 mg</td>
		 <td class='dosechart-method' align='center'>oral</td>
		 <td class='dosechart-substance'><a href='/chemicals/2ci/'>2C-I</a></td>
		 <td class='dosechart-form'><b>(powder / crystals)</b></td>
		</tr>
</table>
<br/>

	<table border='2' cellpadding='4' cellspacing='0' bordercolor='#444455' class='bodyweight'>
	 <tr>
           <td width='110' class='bodyweight-title'>BODY WEIGHT:</td>
	   <td width='80' class='bodyweight-amount'>220 lb</td>
         </tr>
	</table>

<br/><br/>
<!-- End DoseChart  -->
<!-- Start Body -->
My friends and I have been experimenting with 2c-i for the last several weeks.  Our last trip was a good example.  I will describe three psychonauts:<BR>
1.  (Yours truly) A 220-lb male, who took 16mg<BR>
2.  A 180-lb male, 12mg.  Had just done two lines of cocaine. <BR>
3.  A 210-lb male, 17.5 mg <BR>
4.  A 110-lb female, 12mg<BR>
<BR>
All ingested at about 7:30 pm on an empty stomach.  First effects were noted sooner than anticipated at about thirty minutes, manifested by a feeling of energy and a tendency to grin and giggle.  At about 45 minutes, mild nausea was encountered.   Subject 2 vomited once.  (He mentioned that cocaine makes him nauseous at times).  <BR>
<BR>
Visuals started at about the 1 hour mark and were most enjoyable for about 2-3 hours.   A simple pattern on the TV screen seemed to shift and change color.  A rhinestone on subject 4's shoe seemed to be animated.   Subject 3 saw rich patterns in the clouds.  Subject 1 noted that everything seemed to take on an extra dimension.  Pictures seemed three-dimensional.  A Buddha statue seemed alive.<BR>
<BR>
Subjects were for the most part giggly and euphoric.  Subject 2 even with the reduced dose seemed slightly overwhelmed by it all.  Subject 1 noted that it was easy to perceive the emotional state of others, but not easy to vibe with that state necessarily.   <BR>
<BR>
Effects lasted until about 3am.  Difficult to fall asleep.  The next morning, vision seemed off, with poor depth perception.  <BR>
<BR>
Our recommendations:<BR>
<BR>
1.  A peron might have to try this substance at least twice to get a good feel for it.<BR>
2. 12mg is a good dose for a lightweight, 15-17.5 for a big boy.   Enough is as good as a feast.  Take it all at once if you plan to get any sleep at all.  <BR>
3.  If you have a sensitive stomach, think about taking some ginger or cannibis prior to dropping 2c-i.<BR>
4.  Don't even think about driving until 18 h post dose.  <BR>
5.  Alcohol just covers up the effects and makes the trip much less enjoyable.  Cocaine might accentuate the body load.<BR>
6.  Don't take this and go someplace where people fight a lot.  You will consistently underestimate how much your spastically peppy euphoria is irritating the other people at the bar. <BR>
<BR>
Subject 2 was not impressed.  1, 3, and 4 however felt the experience was beautiful.  <BR>
<BR>
This is not a deep experience, or maybe it is.  Here is what I think it all means.  <BR>
<BR>
We live in the midst of almost unbearable beauty, every day, all the time.  We simply choose not to see it.  Look closely at a child's eyes sometime.  They are incredibly bright and clear.  Imagine how beautiful colors look through those eyes.  How amazing a butterfly must seem, through those eyes.  How rich the imagery in clouds.  How brilliant lights are.   That's what it is like.<!-- End Body -->
<br/><br style="clear:both;"/>


